From: retropangui-c5 build <build@retropangui-c5>
Date: Tue, 13 May 2026 00:00:00 +0000
Subject: [PATCH] media: amlogic: add missing DTV_BLIND_SCAN_STEP_NEXT definition

amlfrontend.c references DTV_BLIND_SCAN_STEP_NEXT in a switch-case
statement but this constant is not defined in aml_fe_ext.h, causing
a compilation failure:

  amlfrontend.c:2843:14: error: 'DTV_BLIND_SCAN_STEP_NEXT' undeclared

Add the missing definition after DTV_DELIVERY_SUB_SYSTEM and update
AML_DTV_MAX_COMMAND accordingly.
---
 include/uapi/linux/dvb/aml_fe_ext.h | 3 ++-
 1 file changed, 2 insertions(+), 1 deletion(-)

--- a/include/uapi/linux/dvb/aml_fe_ext.h
+++ b/include/uapi/linux/dvb/aml_fe_ext.h
@@ -67,7 +67,8 @@
 /* Blind scan end*/
 #define DTV_DELIVERY_SUB_SYSTEM			116
-#define AML_DTV_MAX_COMMAND		DTV_DELIVERY_SUB_SYSTEM
+#define DTV_BLIND_SCAN_STEP_NEXT		117
+#define AML_DTV_MAX_COMMAND		DTV_BLIND_SCAN_STEP_NEXT

 #define SYS_ANALOG		(SYS_DVBC_ANNEX_C + 1)
